Metadata.CommitMsg:
Initial commit: Comprehensive 8-Layer DevOps Security Architecture

- 8-layer security scanning: TruffleHog, ClamAV, Checkov, Grype, Trivy, Xeol, SonarQube, Helm
- Dynamic dashboard with real-time security metrics
- Target-aware scanning for specific project directories
- Automated report consolidation and analysis
- HTML/Markdown/JSON multi-format report generation
- AWS ECR authentication integration
- SonarQube test coverage integration (92.38% coverage, 1,170 tests)
- Comprehensive documentation and deployment guides
- Portable scanner for desktop security analysis
Metadata.Author: Ronnie <ronnie.l.nelson10@outlook.com>
